# Nikar, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Nikar (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Khadiyalsky Selsoviet, Tlyaratinsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 3 streets.
Geography
Nikar is located 11&nbsp;km southeast of Tlyarata (the district's administrative centre) by road. Sikar is the nearest rural locality.
